title: Poong, the Joseon Psychiatrist
overview: Yoo Se-poong (Kim Min-jae), a genius doctor, who gets caught up in a royal conspiracy and gets kicked out, meets an eccentric teacher, Gye Ji-han (Kim Sang-kyung) and a widow, Seo Eun-woo (Kim Hyang-gi) of the mysterious and beautiful Gyesu Village, and is reborn as a true doctor.
